{"tid":2374712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府專家暫棄中國科興 藥廠未提交最新資料無法審議","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T14:01:14.000Z","uid":333287,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"458067423bc7de68a4a528a8f5a929d293a7ff6e","tid":2374712,"uid":333287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:18:29.000Z","msg":"本港將展開武肺疫苗接種計劃，衞生防護中心轄下科學委員會的政府專家顧問，就接種群組定下優先次序，最先是院舍院友及職員，第二是醫護人員、其他較高感染風險的必要服務人員，及60歲以上人士，第三是16至59歲長期病患者；但建議只針對料最先到港的德國BioNtech疫苗及將於第二季抵港的阿斯利康疫苗，沒包括中國科興疫苗。委員會指當有更多有關科興的臨床資料會再更新建議。<br />\n疫苗開打︱港府專家暫棄中國科興 藥廠未提交最新資料無法審議.....<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/V5O3AJQSNVHHPNZO2NP56TDZVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FV5O3AJQSNVHHPNZO2NP56TDZVE%2F&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=f741f625\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210121%2FV5O3AJQSNVHHPNZO2NP56TDZVE%2F&h=24a68708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210121/V5O3AJQSNVHHPNZO2NP56TDZVE/</a>"},{"pid":"aaf95c8f96cb3fba6954e27b5d8c61df9780eeb8","tid":2374712,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:19:43.000Z","msg":"因為根本冇效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><p class=\"center\"></p>"},{"pid":"1eac838a6ac90f1aa15d7d64b39be2d92888d476","tid":2374712,"uid":366281,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"仲做緊數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4b71b0221901a56309ed1035f5a80fd7dbec64","tid":2374712,"uid":117622,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"危害國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e1095b38c7b3b721195f790b5b21d36660cecf","tid":2374712,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021